Pull the SMB signal from support and cross-check it against SMB-only survey responses and any SMB onboarding interviews you have. Does "complexity" or "overwhelm" appear across sources? If yes — pattern.
Then ask the structural question: Are these one job at two scopes, or two distinct jobs? (My read: probably one — "I want to feel control over my work without being burdened by every decision" — but you'd validate that with interviews, not infer it from these three sources.)
