The deeper job is mutual accountability transfer — you want the system to ensure landing, not put surveillance on humans. The right solution space is closer to: structured handoffs that require confirmation, decision-confirmation flows, commitment-tracking, or escalation-on-silence patterns. That's where Liam (Hypothesize) should be steered when this hands off.

